M59 P1 Q30 (PF1 RATE)
M51 (CG ON)
G04 P0.2
M53 (PF GAS ON)
G04 P2.0
M55 (PF ON)
G90
G55

%PF Rate
M59 P0 Q25
%CG on
M51
%PF Gas on
M53
G04 P2.0
%PF on
M55
%2 Sec delay
G04 P2.0

